			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Recently on Alt.games.everquest a player asked how each of us would rank the classes in terms of their level of balance.  After seeing some of the responses I realized that it’s completely unreliable for someone who has never played a class to rate it and that there needs to be some criteria to rate by.  With that in mind, I wonder if each of you would mind taking some time out to answer the following poll.  I plan to post the same poll on other class specific boards and post the results when I get them.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Class Balance Criteria
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Answer on a level of 1-5 with 1 being the lowest  (not at all) and 5 being the highest (very much so)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to solo effectively.  Does this class possess the tools to solo with an acceptable experience/downtime ratio to make soloing a viable option for experience gain?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to make money with innate abilities-Does this class possess innate skills or abilities that allow it to make money from other players outside of the melee setting?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to make money through farming-Does this class possess the ability to farm items effectively enough to make it a viable option for making money?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Group contribution- Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a group?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Raid contribution-Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a raid setting?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Self-Sufficiency-Does this class possess the tools to travel safely, get out of trouble or does it have to rely heavily on other classes for survival?  
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Desirability in Groups-Is this a highly desired class for groups?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Perception of Class-How well is this class and the abilities of this class understood by other players?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Equipment-Does this class have a good variety of equipment available to enhance it’s specific abilities?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Expansions and Upgrades-Has this class received helpful new abilities/skills as the game has progressed?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Overall-Is this class properly balanced?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
 <i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
