			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I will give you my point of view from a lvl 65 bst at the high end game.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to solo effectively. Does this class possess the tools to solo with an acceptable experience/downtime ratio to make soloing a viable option for experience gain?: 2
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to make money with innate abilities-Does this class possess innate skills or abilities that allow it to make money from other players outside of the melee setting?: 1
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Ability to make money through farming-Does this class possess the ability to farm items effectively enough to make it a viable option for making money?: 4
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Group contribution- Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a group?: 3
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Raid contribution-Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a raid setting?: 2
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Self-Sufficiency-Does this class possess the tools to travel safely, get out of trouble or does it have to rely heavily on other classes for survival? : 5
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Desirability in Groups-Is this a highly desired class for groups?: 2
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Perception of Class-How well is this class and the abilities of this class understood by other players?: 4
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Equipment-Does this class have a good variety of equipment available to enhance it’s specific abilities?: 2
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Expansions and Upgrades-Has this class received helpful new abilities/skills as the game has progressed?: 2
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Overall-Is this class properly balanced?: 3
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
 Gaturbarsher Feral Lord of Caer Cadarn @ Vazaelle
<br />

<br />
